    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has some noticeable fading in the clear coat on the roof and trunk, along with various small dings and scratches from regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the suspension is a bit noisy over bumps and it will likely need new tires within the next year. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
