    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready and waiting for all your upcoming adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and reinforced subframe mounting points to address common E46 fatigue. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior reflects honest wear consistent with its well-maintained status, while the interior retains its ergonomic integrity. A mechanically sound specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly maintained. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman finished in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic over a Black partial leather interior. This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and serves as a perfect example of a driver-focused sports car that is ready for its next chapter. \n\nExterior: The paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine. While the car presents beautifully, there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel arch\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The 19-inch Cayman S wheels are in excellent shape, with only a very small amount of curb rash on the passenger rear rim. \n\nInterior: Inside, the cabin remains a focused environment. The leather seats show minimal bolster wear on the driver's side, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. Every button, from the dual-zone climate control to the Porsche Communication Management (PCM) system, functions exactly as it should. The carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. \n\nMechanical: This Cayman is mechanically sound and has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers. The 2.0L turbocharged boxer-4 pulls cleanly through the rev range, and the PDK transmission provides crisp, lightning-fast shifts. The tires currently have approximately 60% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last 5,000 miles. \n\nDocumentation: Included in the sale are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts. This is a solid, honest car that delivers the legendary Porsche experience without the 'mint condition' premium.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability and refined engineering. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and long-term durability. The interior remains in excellent order, complemented by a robust mechanical profile that has undergone a rigorous professional inspection. For the driver seeking a sophisticated balance of proven capability and exceptional value, this offering stands as a premier choice in its class.",
      "price": 34800.0,
