      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels wonderful on the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and kept nice and tidy, with a clean interior that makes every drive super comfortable. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
